race.comment: A plain 50 to end the program. SHE'S HIGH SOCIETY (4) is in the premier local stable and looks well placed to win. Won a 58 here and then came back and wasn't beaten far in a 60. Has to lug more weight dropping in grade but can get the job done. PROPHET TIME (9) has been threatening another win and rates well in this line-up. Maps for a soft run and an in-form jockey is engaged. YOU WISH (8) resumes with two trials under the saddle. Flies fresh and finally draws an inside gate. Has the ability and the betting will be key. BEAU ROCK (6) has a handy 2kg claim and races well at home. The veteran will be around the mark.
